# Advanced API Project - Book API

## Overview
This API allows users to manage books using Django REST Framework (DRF).

## Endpoints
| Method | Endpoint          | Description               | Authentication |
|--------|------------------|---------------------------|--------------|
| GET    | /books/          | List all books            | Public |
| POST   | /books/          | Add a new book            | Admin Only |
| GET    | /books/<id>/     | Retrieve a book           | Public |
| PUT    | /books/<id>/     | Update a book             | Admin Only |
| DELETE | /books/<id>/     | Delete a book             | Admin Only |

## Permissions
- **Public:** Can read books.
- **Authenticated Users:** Can create books.
- **Admins:** Can edit/delete books.

